CLM_VALUES.name: CLM_VALUES
CLM_VALUES.description: All values associated with a claim are stored in the Claim External Value record. The CLM_VALUES table holds claim-level values set by the system during claims processing or by user edits.

columns.name: RECORD_ID
columns.description: This column stores the unique identifier for the claim record.

columns.name: BIL_PROV_TYP_QUAL
columns.description: The value indicating whether the billing provider on the claim is a person or a non-person.

columns.name: BIL_PROV_NAM_LAST
columns.description: The billing provider's last name (if a person) or the organization name (if a non-person).

columns.name: BIL_PROV_NPI
columns.description: The billing provider's National Provider Identifier (NPI).

columns.name: BIL_PROV_TAXONOMY
columns.description: The billing provider's taxonomy code.

columns.name: BIL_PROV_TAXID_QUAL
columns.description: The qualifier for the billing provider's tax ID defining the type of ID reported as the tax ID.

columns.name: BIL_PROV_TAXID
columns.description: The billing provider's tax ID. For individuals, this ID could be the SSN or tax ID.

columns.name: BIL_PROV_ADDR_1
columns.description: The first line of the billing provider's street address.

columns.name: BIL_PROV_CITY
columns.description: The billing provider's city.

columns.name: BIL_PROV_STATE
columns.description: The billing provider's state.

columns.name: BIL_PROV_ZIP
columns.description: The billing provider's ZIP Code.

columns.name: CLM_CVG_SEQ_CD
columns.description: The code identifying the filing order for the claim (e.g., primary, secondary, tertiary).

columns.name: CLM_CVG_PYR_NAM
columns.description: The payer name.

columns.name: CLM_CVG_GRP_NUM
columns.description: The group number entered in the coverage record.

columns.name: CLM_CVG_GRP_NAM
columns.description: The group name entered in the coverage record.

columns.name: CLM_CVG_FILING_IND
columns.description: The indicator identifying the type of claim.

columns.name: CLM_CVG_PYR_ID_TYP
columns.description: The qualifier that describes the type of ID used to identify the payer.

columns.name: CLM_CVG_PYR_ID
columns.description: The primary ID for the payer.

columns.name: CLM_CVG_ACPT_ASGN
columns.description: The indicator that the provider accepts assignment from the payer.

columns.name: CLM_CVG_AUTH_PMT
columns.description: The indicator that the insured assigns benefits to the provider.

columns.name: CLM_CVG_REL_INFO
columns.description: The indicator that the insured has authorized the release of information to the payer.

columns.name: PYR_ADDR_1
columns.description: The first line of the payer's street address.

columns.name: PYR_CITY
columns.description: The payer's city.

columns.name: PYR_STATE
columns.description: The payer's state.

columns.name: PYR_ZIP
columns.description: The payer's ZIP Code.

columns.name: PAT_NAM_LAST
columns.description: The patient's last name.

columns.name: PAT_NAM_FIRST
columns.description: The patient's first name.

columns.name: PAT_NAM_MID
columns.description: The patient's middle name.

columns.name: PAT_MRN
columns.description: The patient's medical record number.

columns.name: PAT_REL_TO_INS
columns.description: The patient's relationship to the coverage subscriber.

columns.name: PAT_BIRTH_DATE
columns.description: The patient's birthdate.

columns.name: PAT_SEX
columns.description: The patient's gender.

columns.name: PAT_SIG_ON_FILE
columns.description: The indicator that the patient has signed the necessary release forms and the forms are on file at the provider.

columns.name: PAT_MAR_STAT
columns.description: The patient's marital status.

columns.name: PAT_EMPY_STAT
columns.description: The patient's employment status.

columns.name: PAT_PH
columns.description: The patient's phone number.

columns.name: PAT_ADDR_1
columns.description: The first line of the patient's street address.

columns.name: PAT_CITY
columns.description: The patient's city.

columns.name: PAT_STATE
columns.description: The patient's state.

columns.name: PAT_ZIP
columns.description: The patient's ZIP Code.

columns.name: INV_NUM
columns.description: The invoice number that uniquely identifies the claim in the billing system.

columns.name: ICN
columns.description: The payer's internal control number (ICN) that uniquely identifies the claim in the payer's system.

columns.name: TTL_CHG_AMT
columns.description: The total charge amount for the claim.

columns.name: BILL_TYP_FAC_CD
columns.description: The facility code portion of the bill type (first and second digits).

columns.name: BILL_TYP_FREQ_CD
columns.description: The frequency code portion of the bill type (third digit).

columns.name: ADMSN_TYP
columns.description: The admission type for the claim.

columns.name: ADMSN_SRC
columns.description: The admission source for the claim.

columns.name: DISCHRG_DISP
columns.description: The patient's discharge status, also referred to as the discharge disposition.

columns.name: CLIA_NUM
columns.description: The Clinical Laboratory Improvement Amendment (CLIA) number when the claim contains lab services.

columns.name: OUTSIDE_LAB
columns.description: The indicator that the claim includes purchased services rendered by an independent provider.

columns.name: OUTSIDE_LAB_CHG
columns.description: The price of the purchased services.

columns.name: CLM_FROM_DT
columns.description: The earliest date represented on the claim. This date could be the minimum service date for an outpatient or professional claim or the admission date for an inpatient claim.

columns.name: CLM_TO_DT
columns.description: The latest date represented on the claim. This date could be the maximum service date for an outpatient or professional claim or the discharge date for an inpatient claim.

columns.name: ACDNT_DT
columns.description: The date the automobile accident occurred.

columns.name: ATT_PROV_NAM_LAST
columns.description: The attending provider's last name.

columns.name: ATT_PROV_NAM_FIRST
columns.description: The attending provider's first name.

columns.name: ATT_PROV_NAM_MID
columns.description: The attending provider's middle name.

columns.name: ATT_PROV_NPI
columns.description: The attending provider's National Provider Identifier (NPI).

columns.name: ATT_PROV_TAXONOMY
columns.description: The attending provider's taxonomy code.

columns.name: REND_PROV_TYP
columns.description: The rendering provider on the claim is a person or a non-person.

columns.name: REND_PROV_NAM_LAST
columns.description: The rendering provider's last name (if a person) or the organization name (if a non-person).

columns.name: REND_PROV_NAM_FIRST
columns.description: The rendering provider's first name. It is only populated when the provider is a person.

columns.name: REND_PROV_NAM_MID
columns.description: The rendering provider's middle name. It is only populated when the provider is a person.

columns.name: REND_PROV_NAM_SUF
columns.description: The suffix to the rendering provider's name (e.g., Jr, III). It is only populated when the provider is a person.

columns.name: REND_PROV_NPI
columns.description: The rendering provider's National Provider Identifier (NPI).

columns.name: REND_PROV_TAXONOMY
columns.description: The rendering provider's taxonomy code.

columns.name: REF_PROV_NAM_LAST
columns.description: The referring provider's last name.

columns.name: REF_PROV_NAM_FIRST
columns.description: The referring provider's first name.

columns.name: REF_PROV_NAM_MID
columns.description: The referring provider's middle name.

columns.name: REF_PROV_NPI
columns.description: The referring provider's National Provider Identifier (NPI).

columns.name: REF_PROV_TAXONOMY
columns.description: The referring provider's taxonomy code.

columns.name: SVC_FAC_NAM
columns.description: The name of the external location where the services were performed.

columns.name: SVC_FAC_NPI
columns.description: The NPI of the external location where the services were performed.

columns.name: SVC_FAC_CNCT_PH
columns.description: The contact phone number for the external location.

columns.name: SVC_FAC_ADDR_1
columns.description: The first line of the external location street address.

columns.name: SVC_FAC_CITY
columns.description: The external location's city.

columns.name: SVC_FAC_STATE
columns.description: The external location's state.

columns.name: SVC_FAC_ZIP
columns.description: The external location's ZIP code.

columns.name: CREATE_DT
columns.description: The date the claim was created. It is used for paper institutional claims.

columns.name: CLM_CVG_AMT_PAID
columns.description: The amount already paid by the payer of the current coverage.

columns.name: CLM_CVG_AMT_DUE
columns.description: The amount due by the payer of the current coverage.

columns.name: CLM_CVG_REL_INFO_DT
columns.description: The date on which the insured authorized the release of information to the payer.

columns.name: RECORD_CREATION_DT
columns.description: The date the record was created.

columns.name: CLM_TYP_C_NAME
columns.description: The type of claim values stored in the record. CMS is used for professional and dental claims. UB is used for institutional claims.

columns.name: FORM_TYP_C_NAME
columns.description: The type of form used during processing.

columns.name: SERV_AREA_ID
columns.description: The service area for the claim values record.
